# ============================================
# 8. Traitement des outliers (rgle de l'IQR)
# ============================================

def iqr_winsorize(series, k=1.5):
    """
    Applique une winsorisation base sur l'IQR :
    - Q1, Q3, IQR
    - bornes = [Q1 - k*IQR, Q3 + k*IQR]
    - les valeurs hors bornes sont 'clippes'
    """
    q1 = series.quantile(0.25)
    q3 = series.quantile(0.75)
    iqr = q3 - q1
    lower = q1 - k * iqr
    upper = q3 + k * iqr
    return series.clip(lower, upper)

cols_with_outliers = ["taille", "poids", "revenu_estime_mois", "montant_pret"]

for col in cols_with_outliers:
    if col in df.columns:
        df[col] = iqr_winsorize(df[col], k=1.5)
        print(f"Outliers traits (winsorisation IQR) pour la colonne : {col}")
    else:
        print(f" Colonne {col} absente du dataset.")

# Visualisation rapide aprs traitement
for col in cols_with_outliers:
    if col in df.columns:
        plt.figure(figsize=(6, 3))
        sns.boxplot(x=df[col])
        plt.title(f"Boxplot de {col} aprs winsorisation")
        plt.show()

# ============================================
# 9. Imputation des valeurs manquantes (mthode mdiane)
# ============================================

cols_to_impute = ["historique_credits", "score_credit", "loyer_mensuel"]

for col in cols_to_impute:
    if col in df.columns:
        nb_nan_before = df[col].isna().sum()
        median_value = df[col].median()
        df[col] = df[col].fillna(median_value)
        nb_nan_after = df[col].isna().sum()
        
        print(f"Colonne : {col}")
        print(f" - NaN avant : {nb_nan_before}")
        print(f" - NaN aprs : {nb_nan_after}")
        print(f" - Valeur d'imputation (mdiane) : {median_value:.2f}")
        print("")
    else:
        print(f" Colonne {col} absente du dataset.")

print("Shape final aprs imputation :", df.shape)
print("\nPourcentage de NaN rsiduels par colonne :")
print((df.isna().mean() * 100).round(2))

comparison = stats_before.join(
    stats_after,
    lsuffix="_avant",
    rsuffix="_apres",
    how="inner"
)

print("=== Comparatif AVANT / APRS (moyenne, cart-type, min, max, missing) ===")

    "mean_avant", "mean_apres",
    "std_avant", "std_apres",
    "min_avant", "min_apres",
    "max_avant", "max_apres",
    "missing_pct_avant", "missing_pct_apres"
]])
